{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99719-zhua-zhua-zhua","title":"抓！抓！抓！","description":"马努喜欢蹦跳和数数。但当他得了痒痒的水痘时，事情就麻烦了。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Samidha Gunjal"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99719-zhua-zhua-zhua"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726298/size3/a8d3613af0c68801c935157ee52533a0.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/726298/size6/a8d3613af0c68801c935157ee52533a0.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53528/size6/ba67848f658362d31fb118829cced743.jpg","text":"每天放学后，马努都玩跳房子。\n她跳又数。\n1, 2和 3。\n4, 5和 6。\n7, 8, 9和 10。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53529/size6/669007e7cdeb3b9bdce39c1ba5f9a762.jpg","text":"但今天马努的肚子感觉痒痒的。\n她跳起来并且很重要。 她跳起来，数数。\n1, 2和 3。\n抓！\n4, 5和 6。\n抓！ 抓！\n7, 8, 9和 10。\n抓！ 抓！ 抓！","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53530/size6/c694140a6a8432e45879ea2643c4b653.jpg","text":"她看到小小，痒痒的痘痘。\n1, 2和 3。\n在她的肚子上！\n4, 5和 6。\n在她的怀里！\n7, 8, 9和 10。\n在她背上！\n痒痒的痘痘到处都是！","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53531/size6/1ff549a7296f6d47b6b099a9fa04af94.jpg","text":"“你有水痘，”奶奶说。\n“你不能去上学。”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53532/size6/f8a1c61c20ffe939fce7766afae5333d.jpg","text":"马努趴在床上而开始\n抓！\n抓！ 抓！\n抓！ 抓！ 抓！","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53568/size6/c0a9d5fce4333f2bf1819107d051ae53.jpg","text":"“不要抓它！”奶奶说。\n这使马努更痒！","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53534/size6/0fbde97b3ac22b1733879506d7dab3c6.jpg","text":"当奶奶和爷爷没在看的时候\n抓！\n吃完粥后，\n抓！ 抓！","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53535/size6/2c48afc83c1c101ccc727221cb48cae7.jpg","text":"“别抓！”\n奶奶和爷爷喊。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53536/size6/69957d8f05d06cf6dd8bef1c17563cf4.jpg","text":"但当她躺在床上时，她又，\n抓！\n抓！ 抓！\n抓！ 抓！\n抓！","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53610/size6/fca17524c063a1da736d03a549798c8a.jpg","text":"马努努力试着不去\n抓！ 抓！\n他玩一个叫做蛇和梯子的游戏\n她幻想着许多故事。\n她忘了抓痒！ 抓！","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53569/size6/b5b4a5d179eb0c57f52d59a5af4246b8.jpg","text":"痘痘慢慢的消失了。 马努数着。\n10, 9 和 8。 7, 6 和 5。 4, 3, 2 和 1。\n直到有一天，马努拉起她的衬衫。\n所有痒痒的痘痘都\n不见了！","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53540/size6/b3e2dda7c57d03d33fc309426b86792f.jpg","text":"现在马努可以玩跳房子了。\n她跳又数。\n1, 2 和 3。\n4, 5 和 6。\n7, 8, 9 和 10。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":111}}